FBIS4-9814 "drlat064_o_94002" FBIS-LAT-94-064 Daily Report 1 Apr 1994 Colombia Search `Unsuccessful So Far' Search `Unsuccessful So Far' PA0104223394 Santa Fe de Bogota Emisoras Caracol Network in Spanish 2208 GMT 1 Apr 94 PA0104223394 Santa Fe de Bogota Emisoras Caracol Network Spanish BFN [Text] Santa Fe de Bogota -- The search for Ramon Rissin, Summer Linguistic Institute security chief, has been unsuccessful so far. Alleged FARC [Revolutionary Armed Forces of Colombia] guerrillas allegedly kidnapped him on the road between Puerto Lleras and Loma Linda, where the institute's main office is located.
